commit.message:
fix(models): license attributes;

- Give default values to `od_conformance` and `osd_conformance`.

(cherry picked from commit ab272627e597dad2aec348f21eada4ec85d759cc)

feat(misc): changelog;

- Added change log file.

(cherry picked from commit ba847666a1c5e498bf3dec51eeb35b1c75cf4a6e)

feat(frontend): added change log;

- Added change log file.

(cherry picked from commit c1c156168f167c90afb6a936683b3f6b14d436bc)

feat(frontend): changed null label default return;

- Set return of `get_null_label` helper to blank string.

(cherry picked from commit 470cbf8e67610bf039c6b56174d8fc64a10b1a87)

feat(frontend): moved null label to datatableviews plugin;

- Moved all code from core to datatablesview plugin.

(cherry picked from commit 5315108b5b4e7200a50c7165ccaab48f97c582fc)

feat(frontend): better null label helper;

- Slightly improved return on the `get_helpers` implementation;moved condition into single lambda function.

(cherry picked from commit 260dfaf23548ee6d82a24b0a1ed0d1d7c3b03c12)

fix(syntax): flake8 syntax fix;

- Fixed continual line over-indent.

(cherry picked from commit 2fca690b1f35cc430681bac63ec5dc9dccb545b6)

fix(frontend): helper module syntax fix;

- Fixed flake8 reportings.

(cherry picked from commit 322376e7fef7b07d3efbc67a839637b847c658fd)

feat(frontend): added default value to declaration;

- Added empty string as default value to `ckan.datatables.null_label` declaration.

(cherry picked from commit ecce6bb043f2795146d68bae8f319023ef9a728a)

fix(syntax): fixed flake and pyright issues;

- Removed unused imports.

(cherry picked from commit 9d7c2b81913f0c0fc9f375c0b33e64744f2ac603)

fix(index): solved issues with datastore using validated packages;

- Do not use validated packages to re-index during datastore active flag.
- Removed try/catch.

